quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  7,164,"Nabamwe mu bantu bo muribo mugihe bavuga bati:- hari inyungu nyabaki y’ugutuza abantu Imana izobica canke izohana kubihano bikaze cane, nabo bishuye bati:- turonke ivyitwazo imbere y’Umuremyi wanyu, nkumbure nabo botinya"
  7,165,"Rero mugihe babinegura muvyo bahora bibutswa, twararokoye bamwe bahora batuza amabi, duca duhana bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo kubihano bibi cane mukwiyonkora kwabo"
  7,166,"Mugihe bishima cane nukutareka ivyo twababujije twababwiye duti:- nimube inkende z’ibimaramare"
  7,167,"Mugihe Umuremyi wawe yamenyesha yuko azobazanira kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka abantu bazobahana kubihano bibi cane, mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe aroroshe muguhana kandi ntankeka niyo ifise ikigongwe cinshi c’impuhwe zihagije"
  7,168,"Twaraba tandukanije ng’aha kw’Isi tubagira imirwi itandukanye, kuko muribo harimwo abantu b’intungane, n’abandi muribo n’abatandukanye nabo, natwe twarabahaye ibibazo vyinshi vy’amahirwe hamwe n’amabi, kugira ngo basubire muruhongore"
  7,169,"Munyuma yaho haciye hasubirirwa n’urundi runganwe rubi cane rwatoranye ibisigi vy’igitabu batoramwo ivyabujijwe vyo ng’aha kw’Isi bavuga bati:- twebwe tuzogirirwa ikigongwe n’ibindi nk’ibi nivyadushikira navyone tuzovyakira, mbega ntibagiriwe amasezerano yomu gitabu yuko batazo vuga amajambo bayegeka ku Mana atari ukuri gusa, nabo bakaba baramaze gusoma ibiri muri ico gitabu, n’inzu yo mw’ijuru izobabera nziza muri bamwe batinya Imana yabo y’ukuri, mbega mwebwe ntimutegera"
  7,170,"Nabamwe bafata igitabu c’Imana nka nkama nuguhagarika amasengesho tuzobahenba ineza, mu vy’ukuri natwe ntidutakaza impembo z’abagira ineza"